{"tid":2259864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本九月官方統計: 每300個由中國(非港澳台)入境日本既人就有一個機場檢疫確診武漢肺炎!","createTime":"2020-10-27T06:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T07:23:20.000Z","uid":119393,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfb4f1e158c482c5a1ad887557694e37b7f4c440","tid":2259864,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:59:00.000Z","msg":"唔知香港口岸九月有幾多人入境呢? 哈哈哈哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n九月各國入境日本數字:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jnto.go.jp/jpn/statistics/data_info_listing/xls/201021_monthly.xlsx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jnto.go.jp%2Fjpn%2Fstatistics%2Fdata_info_listing%2Fxls%2F201021_monthly.xlsx&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=320f2289\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jnto.go.jp/jpn/statistics/data_info_listing/xls/201021_monthly.xlsx</a><br />\n<br />\n只抽全球疫情最好(好似係)同最差既中美兩國:<br />\n由中國入境3,000人, 其中10人機場檢疫確診, 中國官方公佈9月全國新症356例<br />\n由美國入境600人, 其中20人機場檢疫確診, 美國官方公佈9月全國新症1,219,954例<br />\n<br />\n明明中美兩國9月官方確診數字相差三千五百倍<br />\n點解響日本機場檢診捉到既確診者只係相差一倍?(如將總入境人數均化則差10倍)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月十宗由中國出發, 日本機場檢疫確診:<br />\n9/2中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13362.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13362.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=11d8c524\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13362.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9/3中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13390.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13390.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=37f511f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13390.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9/4中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13395.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13395.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=30c61e97\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13395.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9/11中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13535.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13535.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=f2d38e84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13535.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9/16中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13644.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13644.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=3bc30a3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13644.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9/20中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13682.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13682.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=7d7cad0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13682.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9/22中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13714.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13714.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=8c5b66bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13714.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9/23中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13738.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13738.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=c3e7ebf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13738.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9/29中國入境確診一人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhlw.go.jp/stf/newpage_13865.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhlw.go.jp%2Fstf%2Fnewpage_13865.html&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=dfb733e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhlw.go.j